Firewalls

zone-based policy firewall
host based
network based



Construct advanced IDS (snort) rules
    Installation Directory
        /etc/snort
    Configuration File
        /etc/snort/snort.conf
    Rules Directory
        /etc/snort/rules
    Rule naming
        [name].rules
    Default Log Directory
        /var/log/snort

-D run snort as daemon
-c specify config file when running snort
-l specify log directory
-r have snort read a pcap file

To run snort as a Daemon
    sudo snort -D -c /etc/snort/snort.conf -l /var/log/snort
To run snort against a PCAP
    sudo snort -c /etc/snort/rules/file.rules -r file.pcap



 sudo snort -D -l /varl/log/snort -c /etc/snort.snort.conf
header info
 sudo tcpdump -r snort.log.<NUMBERS> -XX -vv



























